<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN234-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉai avar pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN234">
<l>nōko yāṉē tēykamā kālai</l>
<l>piṭiyaṭi yaṉṉa ciṟuvaḻi meḻukit</l>
<l>taṉṉamar kātali puṉmēl vaitta</l>
<l>viṉciṟu piṇṭam yāṅkuṇ ṭaṉaṉko</l>
<l>lulakupukat tiṟanta vāyiṟ</l>
<l>palarō ṭuṇṭaṉ marīi yōṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l>  Ah, I ache. May the long time be short.</l>
<l>  How would he eat the sweet little rice ball</l>
<l>  put on the grass by his very beloved</l>
<l>  after cleansing a way short as the leg of a she-elephant,</l>
<l>  he who came together eating with many,</l>
<l>  at the door that was open for the world to enter?</l>
   
</lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
